{"tid":975111,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(理性討論）粵語動畫歌曲","createTime":"2019-01-09T11:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T14:28:01.000Z","uid":82558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"71d5e97d830c173ab6fc27bea9bd56762c45f79f","tid":975111,"uid":82558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:40:02.000Z","msg":"以前TVB播卡通片會用粵語填詞主題曲，造就好多經典，例如不死傳說（鋼之鍊金術師），黃金入球（踢出我天地），系列有數碼暴龍，寵物小精靈，百變小櫻，keroro等等耳熟能詳陪伴我地成長既經典，甚至有兒歌頒獎典禮去推廣粵語動畫歌同詞。不過依家就算tvb播動畫都唔會特意填詞，同時有部分人都好抗拒用粵語填去改原本既日文動畫歌，令到成件事沒落變成極小眾既興趣咁，但原來仲有班人係鍾意填為自己心愛既動畫填粵語詞同唱，捍衛粵語文化，所以想藉此分享下我覺得高質既粵語翻唱作品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先懷緬下以往既經典先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UK05Zxw_z58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUK05Zxw_z58&d=KhbF78JRf%2B7lJ43POXUJH8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=32d64b15\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UK05Zxw_z58</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uV1pNQiQhL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuV1pNQiQhL8&d=KhbF78JRf%2B7lJ43POXUJH8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a22fcb8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uV1pNQiQhL8</a><br />\n近年我覺得高質動畫粵語同人翻唱<br />\n未聞花名- secret base ～君がくれたもの～<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wyEg6tdsm3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwyEg6tdsm3g&d=KhbF78JRf%2B7lJ43POXUJH8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ecb6aac2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wyEg6tdsm3g</a><br />\nfate zero op 2<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FMdRXn_AJ5M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFMdRXn_AJ5M&d=KhbF78JRf%2B7lJ43POXUJH8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=1ccf2948\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FMdRXn_AJ5M</a><br />\n薄櫻鬼黎明錄_ED<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/I2tOFPsMa9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FI2tOFPsMa9s&d=KhbF78JRf%2B7lJ43POXUJH8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a1d8a26e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/I2tOFPsMa9s</a><br />\n鋼之鍊金術師FA<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZhjN4IWvMbw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZhjN4IWvMbw&d=KhbF78JRf%2B7lJ43POXUJH8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=aacc26eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZhjN4IWvMbw</a><br />\n四月是你的謊言ED2<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sKQeHjtbX2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsKQeHjtbX2w&d=KhbF78JRf%2B7lJ43POXUJH8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0d75a519\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sKQeHjtbX2w</a><br />\naLIEz <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7v2_ad41Ciw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7v2_ad41Ciw&d=KhbF78JRf%2B7lJ43POXUJH8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=468da1c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7v2_ad41Ciw</a><br />\n甲賀忍法帖<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SqBoEmyn4mU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSqBoEmyn4mU&d=KhbF78JRf%2B7lJ43POXUJH8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=423b8b8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SqBoEmyn4mU</a><br />\n無論係廣東一帶定香港本土出品都好，希望大家可以抱住開放同學術既角度去討論粵詞，交流並互相學習，推廣粵語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c30337be1d978a46898e5fe7b155efc66656e7","tid":975111,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"偶像活動 op  可以話係tvb近年最高汁動畫op<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2k1UsZW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2k1UsZW.gif&h=bc6ad4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不失日文原版的味道<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cYfWT2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cYfWT2.gif&h=0a0d4c74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hlMJJtbw5Ds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhlMJJtbw5Ds&d=KhbF78JRf%2B7lJ43POXUJH8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=8c5b10ce\" data-auto-l